The presidency has revealed that the president will be meeting with the Fees Must Fall topless students this week.On Tuesday, 3 female protesters at Wits University stripped off their tops and bras outside the Great Hall.According to news sources, They demanded that police officers stop firing rubber bullets and stun grenades at demonstrators gathered on campus this afternoon.This according to news sources caught the president&#8217;s attention and he revealed that he was impressed by their boldness.It is unclear at the moment what the president will discuss with the ladies, but the four will meet at an unnamed hotel in Pretoria before the end of this week.